Set up repo

  $ cat << EOF >> $HGRCPATH
  > [ui]
  > origbackuppath=.hg/origbackups
  > [merge]
  > checkunknown=warn
  > EOF
  $ hg init repo
  $ cd repo
  $ echo base > base
  $ hg add base
  $ hg commit -m "base"

Make a dir named b that contains a file

  $ mkdir -p b
  $ echo c1 > b/c
  $ hg add b/c
  $ hg commit -m "c1"
  $ hg bookmark c1

Peform an update that causes b/c to be backed up

  $ hg up -q 0
  $ mkdir -p b
  $ echo c2 > b/c
  $ hg up --verbose c1
